    "created_at": "2014-09-01T07:02:05Z",
    "updated_at": "2014-09-01T07:02:05Z",
    "body": "The menu implementation in atom-shell used Chromium's menu library, which provided very limited support for dynamic menus and didn't support removing or adding menu items after the menu was created, so there is no simple way to fix this. But after I figured out a way to implement https://github.com/atom/atom-shell/issues/528, this would become possible.\n\nI'm closing this since this is a duplicate of https://github.com/atom/atom-shell/issues/528.\n"
